@startuml
title SensorFusion_Lifecycle
' Owner SWC: SWC_SensorFusion

[*] --> INITIAL
state INIT
state RUNNING
state DEGRADED
state SHUTDOWN

[*] --> INIT : PowerOn
INIT --> RUNNING : InitComplete
RUNNING --> DEGRADED : SensorFailure
DEGRADED --> RUNNING : Recovery
RUNNING --> SHUTDOWN : Shutdown

@enduml